item.title: MrBeast - Protect the Yacht
item.description: Today, MrBeast’s third and last ‘Protect the ___ Keep It’ video released. Another contestant was chosen to defend his yacht using cannons, fireworks, bombs, and fire arrows. Despite some damage, the yacht survived, and the contestant received $50,000 for repairs.

item.title: Game Review | South Park - The Stick of Truth
item.description: In my view, I believe that this game is excellent for any South Park fan. It took me 13 hours to finish the story, yet I still need to complete all the achievements. Despite being released in 2014, it still stands strong in my opinion.
